{"id": "1344459007011717214", "channel_id": "1344459007011717214", "type": 0, "author_id": "1228543639240708178", "author_name": "crownie0406", "author_bot": false, "content": "I want to build a team around her, and is goliath can be pair with her aldo?", "timestamp": "2025-02-27T00:00:06.112000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344459007011717214", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Can anyone please tell me who are the characters that pair well with the red doll?", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842"}
{"id": "1344493579808149585", "channel_id": "1344418250024554496", "type": 19, "author_id": "101202529756385280", "author_name": "teleportingninja", "author_bot": false, "content": "To put it quite simply, there's a lot of different things you can do with traphase, its practically its own game at this point. Based on the characters you've shown here, you can consider things such as a lotan strike team, caecus retal, uvhash bleed, sorel burst/otk, sanga silverheart, jenkins spam (if you have her)", "timestamp": "2025-02-27T02:17:28.909000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1177477727029301321"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1344418250024554496", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344418250024554496", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New To Traphase and want tips.", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1304022948000043028"]}
{"id": "1344493956901240944", "channel_id": "1344418250024554496", "type": 0, "author_id": "101202529756385280", "author_name": "teleportingninja", "author_bot": false, "content": "A lot of traphase is about understanding the various different characters and what they do, and how to counter them, e.g. a silverheart wheel sanga team can be sabotaged by ryker's gunshot posse which randomnises the wheel, or a uvhash bleed team can be countered by characters with purify (such as OG doll), or the staff wheel that clears all debuffs upon exalt", "timestamp": "2025-02-27T02:18:58.815000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344418250024554496", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New To Traphase and want tips.", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1304022948000043028"]}
{"id": "1344494194357436448", "channel_id": "1344418250024554496", "type": 0, "author_id": "101202529756385280", "author_name": "teleportingninja", "author_bot": false, "content": "There's a fairly high amount of freedom on the teams you can kinda craft and mess ard with, so its honestly up to what style you enjoy and knowing how to counter the enemy's gameplan", "timestamp": "2025-02-27T02:19:55.429000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344418250024554496", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New To Traphase and want tips.", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1304022948000043028"]}
{"id": "1344494699565813781", "channel_id": "1344418250024554496", "type": 0, "author_id": "101202529756385280", "author_name": "teleportingninja", "author_bot": false, "content": "Sea festival for example is a great posse for dealing with enemies dependent on exalting, such as jenkins who likes to use the 100 aliemus gain card (which can be cancelled with the void effect). However, if you're dealing with a uvhash which is already fairly close to exalt, it may not be as effective as uvhash has a prep card which he can then spam to quickly gain sufficient aliemus to exalt anyway, or lotan strike teams which uses frenzy and gain so much aliemus void doesn't do much aside from slow them down (so you pray you live through it), and someone or something apply weakness is far more effective", "timestamp": "2025-02-27T02:21:55.880000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344418250024554496", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New To Traphase and want tips.", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1304022948000043028"]}
{"id": "1344494831036137554", "channel_id": "1344418250024554496", "type": 0, "author_id": "101202529756385280", "author_name": "teleportingninja", "author_bot": false, "content": "You can look into <#1326453691527594035> to ask for assistance with team crafting once you have an idea of the kinda teams you wanna go for", "timestamp": "2025-02-27T02:22:27.225000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1344418250024554496", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "New To Traphase and want tips.", "forum_channel_id": "1304022827824844842", "thread_tags": ["1304022948000043028"]}
